body.p: On the 28th October the FSFE Netherlands will have their localgroup meeting. This time it will be held online, so that despite missing our regular physical meeting we keep in touch. The meeting will be from 20:00 until 21:00 CET on the conference server. The meeting will be open for everybody. To join the meeting please send an email to Nico Rikken (nico[dot]rikken[at]fsfe[dot]org), he will send you the meeting link and access code.
